{"tid":813063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墮軌遇正列車駛過　 英一家三口躲坑保命","createTime":"2018-09-10T06:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T07:54:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4cd9f90a4bad43a823d50f7baeab852b779692","tid":813063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180910/20495977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F20495977&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xqxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8db6822a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F20495977&h=42a26861\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180910/20495977</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月10日 <br />\n<br />\n墮軌遇正列車駛過　<br />\n英一家三口躲坑保命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180910/large/a1906a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180910%2Flarge%2Fa1906a.gif&h=0605c345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦地鐵貝克街站（Baker Street）有一家三口墮軌，其間有列車迎頭駛過，三人成功躲在路軌下的坑道生還，被稱為「貝克街的奇蹟」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幸運地未有觸電<br />\n<br />\n英國交通警察局指，事發於上周五晚上10時，一名推着嬰兒車的母親走在貝克街站的銀禧線南行月台上，當時她專注抬頭看列車時間表顯示屏，「沒有留意自己距離月台的邊緣多近，意外地把嬰兒車推過月台」，兩人墮軌後父親跳下軌幫忙，三人逃過一劫數分鐘後警員到場，把他們送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n有看過閉路電視的消息人士指，事發時月台的乘客紛紛「大喊大叫並揮手」指示駕駛員煞停列車，但當列車停下，已經越過三人頭上。他形容這「簡直是奇蹟，他們也很幸運地沒有遭帶電路軌電到」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日泰晤士報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n格魯吉亞分離領袖撞車亡"},{"pid":"e776bccc6072c3fcfd6861ab350eca8dcdbb3784","tid":813063,"uid":19126,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:14:42.000Z","msg":"又係女人on9出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade71f43d1186e03e34243bb3a82ca8ef7b9f7e0","tid":813063,"uid":19613,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"點解英國撚無人屌underground 唔起幕門<br />\n<br />\n但日日有人屌mtr 東鐵無幕門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf71ab7669ba6994427148f508a263616457ee04","tid":813063,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"真係唔死都無用<br />\n好在老公英勇<br />\n如果得個女人 應該慌到就咁車死<br />\n<br />\nbtw 個BB車無事?"},{"pid":"6fecc5ae7ac0a3d14d6fa063242b3d7b2066a31a","tid":813063,"uid":130079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ade71f43d1186e03e34243bb3a82ca8ef7b9f7e0","tid":813063,"uid":19613,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"點解英國撚無人屌underground 唔起幕門<br />\n<br />\n但日日有人屌mtr 東鐵無幕門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"Ching咪撚衝出黎大大聲話比人知你on9得唔得。<br />\n<br />\n事實係求其google下<br />\n連research paper都有得睇<br />\n上網又有討論<br />\n<br />\n同埋香港自己都唔會日日提啦，都係有人跳軌先提下<br />\n<br />\n都唔知ching你係咪on9到精神失常，講野完全脫離現實"},{"pid":"630b97e6e5b57abaea13b9593c4bde90f0075e7b","tid":813063,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連parental care都做唔好學人生仔, 比你避得一次下次咪又係比第部車車死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}